Wishing everyone a happy Kanelbullens dag!

For me it marks the unofficial start of autumn, the best weeks of the year.

Please excuse the state of my buns, my rolling technique leaves a lot to be desired 😆

#cinnamonrolls #kanelbullensdag #baking #hygge #swedish #sweden #homemade #cinnamon #autumn #fall  #sweet #food #foodporn #treats #cosy #homebaking

Some gifts just mean more.

The world so often seems full of bad news and bad decisions - it's hard to maintain positivity.

That's why I think it's so important to value and recognise every privilege and positive happening.

I consider myself incredibly lucky to have had such a kind and generous host in the Faroe Islands. To me, Diana represents a culture of genuine warmth, integrity and generosity - qualities that shine through in craft and creativity.

It is really something different to wear a jumper that has been lovingly stitched by someone you know, or to drink from a cup that was crafted by their very own hands.

Our global mentality of consumption denies us the real, original joy of possession.

Thanks @solbjergdiana for giving me some of my favourite treasures!
